title: Cowboys, Tua Tagovailoa, Tom Brady, Russell Westbrook
itunes:title: Cowboys, Tua Tagovailoa, Tom Brady, Russell Westbrook
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb talks about the latest Dallas Cowboys and QB Dak Prescott situation, why he thinks Dallas should trade up to get QB Tua Tagovailoa, his thoughts on the latest rumors of where QB Tom Brady might end up, and Rockets PG Russell Wesbrook's latest meltdown. Guests include Tony Allen, Shawn Porter, and Brevin Knight.
